
    MAMELODI Sundowns coach Pitso Mosimane is as  angry as a bear with a sore foot following
their disastrous 3-2 loss to Polokwane City on Saturday. And the technical bench boss indicated after their loss that
he was “100% not well”, taking out his infuriation on his misfiring players
who, he said, lacked integrity. “I was saying I would take a point but unfortunately we
lost,” said Mosimane, who saw his charges travel 302km from Chloorkop to
